com.javatoavalla.javascenario.impl

Class ScenarioManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.javatoavalla.javascenario.impl.ScenarioManagerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScenarioManager

    public class ScenarioManagerImpl
extends Object
implements ScenarioManager
    The ScenarioManagerImpl class implements the ScenarioManager interface. It manages the addition of various terms (header, load, set, step, and check) to the Avalla scenario.
